====Usage notes====
In modern standard Chinese, {{zh-l|赤}} is not typically used to mean "red". {{zh-l|紅}}, is used instead.
: Examples:
: {{zh-usex|我 買 了 一個 '''紅''' 蘋果。|I bought a '''red''' apple.}}
: {{zh-usex|'''紅'''色 是 用作 危險 的 警告 色。|'''Red''' is used as a warning colour of danger.}}

{{zh-l|赤}} is more commonly used in slogans, poem and coinages to mean red.
: Examples:
: {{zh-usex|'''赤'''色政權|communist regime (literally: '''''red''' regime'')}}
: {{zh-usex|'''赤'''色 的 晚霞|'''red''' sunset clouds}}
: {{zh-usex|'''赤'''字|deficit (literally: '''''red''' figures/numbers'')}}

